title: Liverpool player ratings: Stars flop but one unexpected ace leaves Leicester with pride
text:
1 of 11 Simon Mignolet - 6: One of the better performers despite conceding three 
Liverpool were humiliated with a 3-1 defeat at the hands of managerless Leicester City at the King Power Stadium. 
Many of Jurgen Klopp's top stars were off the boil, though one unexpected player could leave the field with some credit.
